---
title: Baked Cheesy Chicken and Spinach 'Taquitos' with Zesty Tomato Salad
description: Taquitos are a traditional Mexican street food which are normally deep fried. We’ve baked ours instead to give it a healthy twist! They should crisp nicely in the oven while the cheesy centre melts. Get excited because they’re delicious!
